bpp/descriptor.short_desc: Heritage Groceries is a celebrated name in the dairy industry, renowned for its commitment to delivering premium dairy products that embody freshness, quality, and health.
bpp/descriptor.long_desc: Heritage Groceries is a celebrated name in the dairy industry, renowned for its commitment to delivering premium dairy products that embody freshness, quality, and health. With a rich legacy rooted in traditional farming practices and modern innovation, Heritage Groceries has established itself as a trusted brand for families across the nation.

@ondc/org/statutory_reqs_prepackaged_foo.nutritional_info: No preservatives | No added artificial flavours & colours | No chemicals | No refined sugar | No maida bsicuits | Eggless | 100 % Vegetarian
@ondc/org/statutory_reqs_prepackaged_foo.additives_info: Preservatives,made up of oats atta/flour, jowar whole grain, dry fruits like walnuts (akrot), dry cranberry, raisins (kishmish), sunflower seeds, pumpkin seeds, and organic jaggery.

descriptor.long_desc: Heritage Sweet lassi instantly refreshes yourself on a hot day. It is made with freshly churned curd and hint of Cardamom & Vanilla. Bringing you a delightful mix of rich and creamy goodness in every sip.

@ondc/org/statutory_reqs_prepackaged_foo.nutritional_info: Mix of rich and creamy goodness.
